scene.message:
Yukino: Huh.........{nl}
So that's the "reason" you{nl}
had no choice but to shut{waitkey}yourself in a dream world.{waitkey}{clearbox}......And so what?{waitkey}{ret}

Kumi: Y-you... you saw that{nl}
and feel nothing? Wh-what's{nl}
wrong with you?{waitkey}{clearbox}The Sn-Snow Queen... the mask{nl}
understood my pain and{nl}
sorrow right away...!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Y-you're just like my{nl}
father and those drama{nl}
club people!{waitkey}{clearbox}From the very start, you've{nl}
never even tried to{nl}
understand me!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Honestly...!{nl}
You fled into a dream world{nl}
over a reason that trivial,{waitkey}that worthless?{waitkey}{clearbox}It's too absurd for words.{nl}
You... you're making a{nl}
mockery of life, aren't you?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Heyyy! Kumi-chan,{nl}
you're overthinking life{nl}
way too much,{waitkey}aren't you?{waitkey}{clearbox}...I mean, c'mon!{nl}
Life is nothing but{nl}
fun stuff!{waitkey}{clearbox}Really! Let's keep it{nl}
breezy, breezy - just{nl}
like me!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: What's that?!{nl}
So you just wanted to brag{nl}
you're good at studying!{waitkey}{clearbox}Fine, Ayase's an idiot!{nl}
Ugh, unbelievable!{waitkey}So annoying!{waitkey}{ret}

Kumi: But... but...!{nl}
What did I ever do?{nl}
No matter what I do or don't!{waitkey}{clearbox}Nobody ever says a kind{nl}
word to me! And I,{nl}
in my own way,{waitkey}{clearbox}I tried my best! But the{nl}
people around me! The people{nl}
around me! Hey! Lord Hypnos!?{waitkey}{clearbox}Hey!? It's true, right?!{nl}
I'm not the one at fault,{nl}
am I?{waitkey}{ret}

Hypnos: Just so!{nl}
Kumi's not at fault!{nl}
The one at fault is...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ..."Other people,"{nl}
is it? Hmph. How easy your{nl}
way of living has been...{waitkey}{clearbox}All you had to do was blame{nl}
everything on everyone else{nl}
and keep running away!{waitkey}{clearbox}And then, tired of even{nl}
running, now you play alone{nl}
in a dream world?{waitkey}{clearbox}In the end, you fled to a{nl}
dream world, afraid to face{nl}
the real world and people.{waitkey}A loser, aren't you?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: "Other people"?{nl}
How easy your way of{nl}
living is...{waitkey}{clearbox}Blaming everything on others{nl}
while you complain from{nl}
the safety zone...{waitkey}{clearbox}Are you really so afraid{nl}
of dealing with{nl}
other people?{waitkey}{clearbox}You truly are a selfish,{nl}
weak person, aren't you.{waitkey}{ret}

Kumi: Who do you think you{nl}
are?! All of you!{nl}
I'm happy as I am now!{waitkey}I'm happy, I tell you!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Only the Snow Queen's mask!{nl}
Only Lord Hypnos!{nl}
They alone saved me!{waitkey}{clearbox}In the dream world, for the{nl}
first time! The first time,{nl}
I gained my freedom!{waitkey}{clearbox}Even if the world itself is{nl}
a dream, this "happiness"{nl}
in my heart{waitkey}alone is real!{waitkey}{ret}

Hypnos: Enough!{nl}
It's... enough, Kumi.{nl}
Let's finish them off.{waitkey}{clearbox}And return to our happy{nl}
dream, just the two of us.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Drop the tough act.{nl}
This is the "Anti-Dream{nl}
World," right?{waitkey}{clearbox}Then you two here are just{nl}
phantoms created by the dream{nl}
of "Kumi Hirose," who's{waitkey}somewhere in this tower, yeah?{waitkey}{clearbox}Which means if we pinch you{nl}
awake, you'll vanish -{nl}
that's how it works,{waitkey}isn't it!{waitkey}{clearbox}I'll wake you right now!{nl}
Rub those sleepy eyes,{nl}
'cause here we come.{waitkey}Wash your neck and wait!!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: So that Kumi girl{nl}
is the boss of this tower!{waitkey}{clearbox}She must be holding a{nl}
"Mirror Shard" or two{nl}
as well.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Boo! Boo!!{nl}
What an infuriating woman.{nl}
Let's take her down quick!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: What is with that{nl}
woman! I can only call it{nl}
making a mockery of life.{waitkey}{clearbox}Her mistaken victim mentality,{nl}
"I alone am unfortunate,"{nl}
doesn't sit well with me.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Hmm...{nl}
Life sure is tough...{nl}
I'm smart and I've struggled,{waitkey}{clearbox}so I kinda get how{nl}
Kumi-chan feels.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: That "Hypnos" beside{nl}
Kumi... a phantom of an{nl}
ideal "prince" born of{waitkey}{clearbox}Kumi's dream... I do hope{nl}
it's merely a creation.{waitkey}{ret}

Kumi: Wh-what is it!{nl}
L-lay a hand on me, and{waitkey}{clearbox}L-Lord Hypnos won't{nl}
stay silent!{waitkey}{ret}

Kumi: A w-wise choice.{nl}
Had you pinched me, things{nl}
would have gotten ugly.{waitkey}{ret}
